{"questionId":"22253","questionHtml":"<p>Hence or otherwise, determine the value of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><munder><mi>lim</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>9</mn></msup></mfrac></mfenced></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>attempt to substitute&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>≈</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;into&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>9</mn></msup></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>9</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>≈</mo><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mn>3</mn></msup><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>9</mn></msup></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<